{"id":11843,"date":"2024-03-20T14:47:47","date_gmt":"2024-03-20T09:17:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/?p=11843"},"modified":"2024-03-30T12:01:01","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T06:31:01","slug":"how-to-manage-products-listing","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/how-to-manage-products-listing\/","title":{"rendered":"How to Manage Products Listing"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. <\/strong>\u091c\u093e\u0928\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Products List<\/mark> \u0915\u094b \u0915\u0948\u0938\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Manage<\/mark> \u0915\u0930\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Products Option \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a-\u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 Products \u0915\u094b Manage \u0906\u0936\u093e\u0928\u0940 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u094b \u092d\u0940 Products \u0906\u092a\u0928\u0947 list \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0939\u094b\u0964 <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0907\u0938\u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925-\u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0914\u0930 \u092d\u0940 \u092c\u0939\u0941\u0924 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"><strong>Option Products Manage<\/strong><\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092e\u093f\u0932\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u093f\u0928\u0915\u093e \u0907\u0938\u094d\u0924\u0947\u092e\u093e\u0932 \u092c\u0939\u0941\u0924 \u0906\u0936\u093e\u0928\u0940 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u091c\u093e \u0938\u0915\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u094b \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 Products  \u0915\u094b \u0939\u092e\u0947\u0936\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Up-To-Date<\/mark> \u0930\u0916\u0928\u0947 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0915\u0930\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0947\u0902 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Products Function<\/mark> \u0915\u0948\u0938\u0947 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0915\u0930\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"139\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-1024x139.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11845\" style=\"width:582px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-1024x139.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-500x68.png 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-768x105.png 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:28% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"581\" height=\"147\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11849 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-3.png 581w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-3-500x127.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 581px) 100vw, 581px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-black-color\">1.<\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> Search Products: <\/mark>&#8211; Search Products \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e List \u0915\u093f\u092f\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 Products \u0915\u094b \u0916\u094b\u091c \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:15%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"191\" height=\"95\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240315-190614-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11847\" style=\"width:163px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:85%\">\n<p>2. <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Scanner: &#8211; <\/mark>Scanner \u0915\u0947 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e \u0906\u092a \u0915\u093f\u0938\u0940 \u092d\u0940 Products \u0915\u094b \u0906\u0936\u093e\u0928\u0940 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Products List \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0938\u093e\u092e\u0940\u0932 \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"595\" height=\"549\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Digital-marketing-course-with-placements-595-x-549-px-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11859\" style=\"width:430px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Digital-marketing-course-with-placements-595-x-549-px-1.png 595w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Digital-marketing-course-with-placements-595-x-549-px-1-500x461.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"grid-template-columns:34% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"986\" height=\"713\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240319-013724-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11851 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240319-013724-1.png 986w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240319-013724-1-500x362.png 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240319-013724-1-768x555.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 986px) 100vw, 986px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<ol>\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"><strong>Sort By (A To Z): &#8211;<\/strong><\/mark> List \u0915\u093f\u092f\u0947 \u0917\u092f\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 Products \u0915\u094b Latter Wise \u0930\u0916\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964<mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-black-color\">Example:-<\/mark><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark>\u0915\u0947 \u0924\u094c\u0930 \u092a\u0930,  <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">&#8220;A&#8221;<\/mark> <\/strong>\u0928\u093e\u092e  \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u091c\u094b \u092d\u0940 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Products Starts<\/mark> \u0939\u094b\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0909\u0928\u0915\u094b \u090f\u0915 \u0915\u094d\u0930\u092e \u092e\u0947 \u0926\u0947\u0916\u093e\u092f\u093e \u091c\u093e\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0909\u0936\u0940 \u0924\u0930\u0939 <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">&#8220;B&#8221;<\/mark><\/strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <\/mark>\u0928\u093e\u092e \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0947 Product \u0915\u094b \u090f\u0915 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0930\u0916\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0914\u0930 \u092f\u0947 \u0908\u0938\u0940 \u0915\u094d\u0930\u092e \u092e\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 Products \u0915\u094b last \u0924\u0915 \u0930\u0916\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964                                                                                <br><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Sort By (Z To A): &#8211;<\/mark> <\/strong>Z To A \u0915\u094d\u0930\u092e \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 Product \u0915\u094b Show \u0915\u0930\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964<br> <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong> <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Sort By Price (Low To High): <\/mark>&#8211;<\/strong> Sort Price \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0909\u0928 Products \u0915\u094b \u0926\u093f\u0916\u093e\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u093f\u0928\u0915\u093e \u0926\u093e\u092e \u0938\u092c \u0938\u0947 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0939\u094b\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u092e\u0924\u0932\u092c \u092f\u0947 \u0915\u093f \u0909\u0928 Products \u0915\u094b \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u092e\u0928\u0947 \u0932\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948 \u091c\u093f\u0928\u0915\u093e \u0926\u093e\u092e \u0938\u092c \u0938\u0947 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0939\u094b\u0924\u0